snippet.title: The Void Rains Upon Her Heart - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
The Void Rains Upon Her Heart is a boss rush, Bullet-hell game where you control the heart of an alien girl as she tries to befriend bizarre monsters. Coming to Steam early access on Feb 14th, 2018.

You can try the alpha demo for this game right now at http://www.veyeralgames.com/
